<li><a href="/wiki/Modulation" title="Modulation">Modulation</a> — for an overview of all modulation schemes</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Phase_modulation" title="Phase modulation">Phase modulation</a> (PM) — the analogue equivalent of PSK</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Polar_modulation" title="Polar modulation">Polar modulation</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/PSK31" title="PSK31">PSK31</a></li>
